title: Tim's Last Words
author: Rykleos
pages:
#- So you've found this 
book, eh? It's probably been many years since I buried this, and I'm probably long gone. I have to get a few things off my chest: 

1. I didn't mean to kill John. It just sort of happened. Spur of the moment.
#- 2. I did it for Susan. That asshole kept abusing her, and I couldn't stand it. So I killed him.

I still have the money. The money I won from the lottery.

It's located at -5038, 68, 1877.
Tell Susan I love her.
#- 